channel.title: Looking for an extra hand for coders
channel.description:
Looking for an extra hand on deck for my server, VPS and Website are paid for as of now.
Looking for at least a decent amount of experience, someone that can become a friend of us all (the community) easily, and just someone who will be laid back but work when needed.
PM me for further discussion, thank you.
